x.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-053.jpg?height=427&width=401&top__y=980&top__x=468","line":1060,"embedded":true},{"title":"|764x188","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-055.jpg?height=256&width=1043&top__y=1369&top__x=362","line":1091,"embedded":true},{"title":"0, \\frac{\\sqrt{5}}{5}\\.$ )；\n(4) $\\triangle F M N$ 周长的最小值为 $\\sqrt{2}+1$.\n\n其中正确结论的为（）\nA. (1)(2)\nB. (2)(3)\nC. (3)(4)\nD. (1)(4)\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-078.jpg?height=427&width=404&top__y=980&top__x=466","line":1534},{"title":"2,+\\infty)$\nD. $(-\\infty, 2) \\cup(2,+\\infty)$\n\n#### 10.2.2 【 练 1-1\n\n圆 $x^{2}+y^{2}+4 \\sin \\theta \\cdot x+4 \\cos \\theta \\cdot y+1=0$ 的半径等于 $\\qquad$ .\n\n#### 10.2.3 【 练 1-2\n\n已知 $A(-2,2) ， B(2,6)$ ，则以 $A B$ 为直径的圆的标准方程为 $\\qquad$ .\n\n#### 10.2.4 【 练 1-3\n\n正方形草地 $A B C D$ 边长 $1.2 ， E$ 到 $A B ， A D$ 距离为 $0.2 ， F$ 到 $B C ， C D$ 距离为 0.4 ，有个圆形通道经过 $E ， F$ ，且与 $A D$ 只有一个交点，求圆形通道的周长 $\\qquad$ . (精确到 $0.01)$\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-118.jpg?height=318&width=304&top__y=889&top__x=299","line":2226},{"title":"                                                             | 201x197","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=197&width=201&top__y=1293&top__x=738","line":2683,"embedded":true},{"title":"                                                             | 212x197","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=197&width=212&top__y=1513&top__x=723","line":2684,"embedded":true},{"title":"                                                             | 201x156","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=156&width=201&top__y=1742&top__x=738","line":2685,"embedded":true},{"title":"|401x429","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-161.jpg?height=429&width=401&top__y=982&top__x=468","line":3034,"embedded":true},{"title":"50,60$ ) 内的人数为 16 ，则下列结论正确的是（）\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-185.jpg?height=435&width=618&top__y=1781&top__x=296","line":3503}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"1c51oxn","at":1771320748529}},"smart_blocks:01-数学教学/讲义/09-讲义汇总/XDF讲义/FY25 高三数学秋季【行远班教材】修改版本.md#": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05611489,-0.00202275,0.05234649,-0.00140454,0.02713291,-0.01082917,-0.05136544,0.01636518,0.02855873,0.05872566,0.02247684,-0.05942832,0.03511079,0.00637186,0.00164011,-0.00402366,-0.01062966,-0.04473716,-0.0356332,-0.01596685,0.13167638,-0.02120232,-0.0142917,-0.06282023,0.05717664,0.04180922,0.00316701,-0.07046834,-0.02293929,-0.20124947,-0.01584849,0.0830983,0.05429359,0.02900012,0.04332811,-0.04411885,-0.00691252,0.07332761,-0.01502204,0.05728075,0.00029584,0.07399389,-0.00126024,0.00183268,0.00147328,-0.08219094,-0.03269747,-0.02185486,0.032696,-0.03930034,-0.02606218,-0.03655713,0.00166172,0.03766361,-0.0126744,0.00116107,0.05117925,0.02385944,0.00997716,0.01533798,0.00865008,0.00188666,-0.24244359,0.05915261,0.06061313,-0.03895342,-0.02545767,-0.03561111,0.02614065,0.07691722,-0.03611358,-0.01505924,-0.00335782,0.00246011,-0.01406933,-0.02802668,0.00130774,-0.0882954,-0.01285367,-0.06676947,-0.00509465,0.09739108,-0.02782565,-0.02044553,0.00031923,0.02884947,0.00343505,-0.07929214,-0.00220175,-0.03708797,0.00665163,-0.02709033,-0.00374482,0.01540482,-0.07656477,-0.03612025,0.01331726,0.01788658,-0.02039514,0.08294731,-0.04655424,0.02129623,0.04513694,0.00686432,-0.03335876,0.02874554,-0.00186425,-0.08993375,-0.02888811,-0.01885132,-0.02617091,0.00911542,0.10064372,-0.01762103,-0.01223301,0.00136206,-0.00352943,-0.02421203,-0.0117472,0.0419655,-0.00897865,0.0143025,0.02724005,-0.02527958,0.03628483,-0.02652456,-0.0041661,0.01802933,0.01886011,0.03980642,0.04014151,-0.01270273,-0.04458